{"tid":585772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性討論] 到底的士嘅行李收費係何解？","createTime":"2018-03-09T03:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T05:50:24.000Z","uid":10666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"48988e19fbff6ccbe36ec448d8bbb8658c16a9a7","tid":585772,"uid":10666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:13:25.000Z","msg":"今日坐的士嘅時候，忽然腦中出現一個問題<br />\n<br />\n到底的士6蚊嘅行李收費係因為d乜野而收？<br />\n<br />\n係因為重量會影響行車用油？定係因為其他原因？<br />\n<br />\n我有諗過會唔會係因為司機會落車幫手搬行李，所以係搬運費，但我亦記得幾個月前有個港女開post屌個司機唔幫佢搬行李比人圍屌，有巴打話司機落車幫你搬係人情唔係奉旨，咁即係話都唔係搬運費喇<br />\n<br />\n咁到底呢6蚊收費嘅原因係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"ffbc4f831279c23ac6de85aa0cfc8450df47214c","tid":585772,"uid":10666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/111353_1c28b8c44043ba77cd20d9a355dcd3cf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F111353_1c28b8c44043ba77cd20d9a355dcd3cf.png&h=98423ce9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係有坐的士"},{"pid":"befeda84fc23cebd0885f718fa9dc2ad46727890","tid":585772,"uid":71315,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:14:42.000Z","msg":"凍飲點解要加錢？"},{"pid":"ff804144fae06504b262ae865ccfe8e7d74f483a","tid":585772,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:15:05.000Z","msg":"巧立名目"},{"pid":"6de52a5356439c80477973294a6715df169f5de4","tid":585772,"uid":120627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"befeda84fc23cebd0885f718fa9dc2ad46727890","tid":585772,"uid":71315,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:14:42.000Z","msg":"凍飲點解要加錢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:15:47.000Z","msg":"因為要加冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5142dd9e5188907ac